info.text: Helpful products in light of COVID-19
All of the Square apps, products, and services you use can be found here.
By subscribing to Square for Retail, you’ve unlocked new tools in the app menu to manage your retail business.
Simply click and hold on any app, then drag and drop to organize them in the way that works best for you.
This Setup Guide will take you through the steps needed to get My Business up and running on Square.
Activate your account to take payments
Get started with Square Point of Sale
Use the search icon to look for specific pages or topics within your Dashboard.
You can access your account settings and business details here.
You can take the Dashboard tour anytime by going here.

Your funds will only be transferred into a verified bank account. Verification usually takes a few minutes, but for some banks can take up to 4 business days. If you change bank accounts, your money will continue to be transferred into your existing account until the new account is verified.
Once your bank account is verified, card payments are transferred into your account in 1-2 business days. Online sales are transferred the day after you complete the order.
